        <!-- 8. 法律護身符 -->
        <section id="section-7" class="my-16 md:my-24">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-white text-center"><span class="accent-color">七、</span>法律的利劍：你的護身符</h2>
            <p class="text-center text-gray-400 mb-8">這些冰冷的條文，正是界定是非、裁決責任、保護你我權益的最後防線！讀懂它們，運用它們，才能在這場博弈中立於不敗之地！</p>
            <div id="laws-accordion" class="space-y-3">
                 <!-- Law Item -->
                <div class="law-item card rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <button class="law-header w-full text-left p-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-[#1d3b61] transition">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">《金融消費者保護法》</span>
                        <span class="law-icon text-xl accent-color transition-transform duration-300">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="law-content hidden p-4 border-t border-gray-700">
                        <p class="text-gray-300">核心作用：保障您在購買金融商品時的公平待遇與資訊透明權利。</p>
